/****** Object:  StoredProcedure [dbo].[GetNextUniqueID]    Script Date: 05/22/2013 11:19:33 ******/
/******************************************************************************                      
** Name:     GetNextUniqueID                      
** Short Desc: Increments and returns unique value counters in UniqueID  Table. Next value is returned in the @Result out parameter
**                      
** Full Description: Increments and returns unique value counters in UniqueID  Table. Next value is returned in the @Result out parameter
**                              
** Input Arguments:   @IDType - Type of Counter to increment.
**    @Result - OUT parameter for returning next ID in sequence. 
**    @VB     - Boolean flag to return VB recordset.                                 
** Sample Call     
**                           
**                      
